column1: Note: If you have a conflict, please speak to your instructors. All conflicts must be resolved between the instructors and the student.

To filter data, click the drop-down arrow on the column you want to filter: 
- Use the search box to find specific values.
- Check or uncheck boxes next to the values you want to filter.
- Select "Add current selection to filter" to add to your class list.
If you can't find your class, try typing the first few letters, and it should show up in the filter selection.
